## âœ¨ Features

* âš¡ Async Python SDK (aiohttp based)
* ğŸ–¥ï¸ Built-in CLI (`brokenx`)
* ğŸ”‘ Secure API-key authentication
* ğŸµ Audio & ğŸ¬ Video support
